# Vibage (Cursor entry)

Product SSOT: vibage-skills package. Skills under `~/.cursor/skills/vibage-*` (and optional project `.cursor/skills/`).

## Skill routing

1. No `docs/vibage/STATUS.md` → **vibage-init**
2. Hub ready, no valid CONFIRM → **vibage-orient**
3. CONFIRM OK → **vibage-locate**
4. NEW-CHAT / install unclear → **vibage-bootstrap** or **vibage-init**
5. SelfAutoBuz hub hygiene → **docs-hygiene** (not vibage-locate)

## PKG_ROOT

```bash
bash /path/to/vibage-skills/scripts/resolve-pkg-root.sh
```

Probe order includes `~/.cursor/skills`, `~/.claude/skills`, `~/.agents/skills`.

